独家 | 第一批上海援鄂医疗队领队郑军华：重症患者治疗已经积累一些经验。
Cheng Junhua, leader of the first Shanghai medical team, has accumulated some experience in the treatment of severe patients.
周 洁。
Zhou Jie.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
